<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Lee Byrne</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Lee Byrne — hi.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Lee Byrne">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Lee Byrne — hi.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f8f7f5;
      --fg: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #6b6b6b;
    }

    html { background: var(--bg); }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    main {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .content {
      max-width: 36rem;
      width: 100%;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .wave {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
      transform-origin: bottom right;
      animation: wave 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes wave {
      0%, 60%, 100% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      10%, 30% { transform: rotate(14deg); }
      20% { transform: rotate(-8deg); }
      40% { transform: rotate(-4deg); }
      50% { transform: rotate(10deg); }
    }

    .bio {
      font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 32rem;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    li {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    li strong {
      color: var(--fg);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .links a {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--fg);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 4px;
      text-decoration-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.2);
      transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .links a:hover {
      text-decoration-color: var(--fg);
    }

    footer {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>hi, I'm Lee <span class="wave">👋</span></h1>

      <p class="bio">I do revenue ops in healthcare by day. By 2027, I plan to do considerably less of that.</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>currently:</strong> counting down</li>
        <li><strong>based in:</strong> somewhere with weather</li>
        <li><strong>collecting:</strong> hobbies for retirement</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="mailto:hello@leebyrne.com">email</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <span>leebyrne.com</span>
    <span id="year"></span>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
